---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn about NameGen and why we built this free name generator tool."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#111111] dark:text-white">About NameGen</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[#666666] dark:text-[#888888] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        NameGen was created by a small group of writers, gamers, and developers who got tired of hitting creative blocks when searching for character names, business brands, or new pet identities.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our goal was simple: to build a lightning-fast, privacy-first, and clean-looking name generator that doesn't bombard you with popups, signups, or heavy loading delays.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Why Use NameGen?</strong>
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Privacy First:</strong> Your favorites list is stored strictly on your device. We don't save your keystrokes or track your selections on a server.</li>
        <li><strong>Zero Cost:</strong> The site is 100% free to use.</li>
        <li><strong>Minimalist Design:</strong> Focused on names and names only. Simple flat aesthetics that load instantly and look premium.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
